originalText.text: This venue, staff and management was amazing for a recent event we held at Helen Mills. Maria is exceedingly organized and communicative. They went above and beyond for all of our needs and requests, even renting out additional AV equipment the night before to ensure everything went smoothly. Would definitely recommend this venue!

originalText.text:
A wonderful venue, theater, and top notch staff! This venue is great for women's networking or empowerment gatherings.

Emily, Melissa, Brittany, Kyle, the security staff, coat check girl, and AV were all on point!!  Attendees were impressed with the service and attention to detail.

Helen, you have some wonderful people working for you! It was a pleasure meeting you! We will surely be back! Thank you!

originalText.text: Nice open space with hardwood floors and a decent bar. The theater/stage downstairs is pretty nice and seats 160. During a crowded event, the flow of walking traffic is difficult because it's somewhat narrow and there are no alternate routes.

originalText.text: Thanks to Maria, Brianna, Mark, Helen and everyone for the most amazing wedding reception ever!  The guests had such a wonderful time and commented on the beautiful space, fantastic food, drink, ambiance, service. It was perfection!

originalText.text:
Absolutely amazing! The best venue I have ever worked with, extremely helpful and personalized service. The Helen Mills staff really goes out of their way to make sure your event is perfect. They worked with us and put together a 140 person event within 2 weeks. The process was extremely smooth and they were upfront about all cost and were great at making recommendations and finding solutions.

The event space is beautiful and versatile. Great flexibility with lighting and design. Anything you can think of, Helen Mills can help you make it a reality.
Thank you to the entire Helen Mills Team for making our night great!
